Featuring an integrated pump, this reliable shower boosts water flow while its patented bi-metallic cartridge makes use of thermostatic technology for safe precision mixing of hot and cold water. Supplied with an adjustable showerhead, the Aquastream gives users total control over their showering comfort with separate flow and temperature dials and a choice of two flow settings, from a gentle 10LPM to an intense 18LPM. Surface-mounted, Aquastream showers are easy to install, minimising the need for re-tiling.

Title: Mira Advance ATL low pressure 9.0kw
Description: Combining safety and intuitive usability, the 9kW Mira Advance ATL electric thermostatic shower incorporates a range of accessibility features including tactile areas, audible navigation and large backlit buttons for peace of mind showering, as well as thermostatic temperature control and adjustable temperature limit with eight maximum temperature settings. Featuring an integral pump for performance at low pressure and on/off push button for easy select-and-forget use, the A-rated Advance ATL is easy to operate and just as easy to clean.

Title: Triton Omnicare Ultra electric shower 8.7kW
Description: Simply safe and stylish, the Triton Omnicare Ultra electric shower is designed to be easily used by all, no matter the level of assistance required. To achieve this, Omnicare Ultra employs precise thermostatic control, audible confirmations and a tactile temperature dial. Additionally, this accessible and flexible pack includes an extended rail kit for practical seated use and remote start/stop for easier assisted showering.

Title: Triton Omnicare thermostatic electric shower with grab rail 8.5kW
Description: BEAB Care Mark approved, the Triton Omnicare 8.5kW thermostatic electric shower with grab rail blends safety with style for a shower that fits any home. Fitted with a wide range of accessibility features, including a grey toned dial and soft-touch start/stop button, this shower also offers reliable safety via its scald-free thermostatic control, keeping the selected temperature within a single degree. An extended riser rail and longer length shower hose meanwhile make the Omnicare suitable for both seated and standing showering.

Title: Aqualisa eVolve grey/satin silver 10.5kW
Description: Combining style and quality in a robust package, the streamlined Aqualisa eVolve electric shower has a modern Space Grey casing with a contoured silver satin trim. Offering flexible installation, this modern unit is a suitable retrofit for most older electric showers thanks to multi-fit connection options while connection to an existing cold water supply at 240V is simple. With a variety of power settings and three spray patterns, this 10.5kW shower provides the perfect shower experience for everybody and every situation. Meanwhile, individual temperature control along with a digital temperature display allows for smooth, precise adjustment. For safety and practicality, the eVolve incorporates an over-temperature stop function as well as an automatic phased shutdown to reduce the build-up of limescale.
